snippet.title: Comet - Reveal Trailer | Playdate Game
snippet.description:
☄Comet -  A Light-hearted puzzle adventure!
Catalog Page: https://play.date/games/comet/
Itch Page: https://guv-bubbs.itch.io/comet

Made by Team Comet
Donald Bubbins Fraser - Project lead
Drew Loebach - Programming lead
Maria - Art lead
William Aryitey - Narrative lead

Trailer Support
Kirill / Xmenekai -  Cutscene Artist
Choosh - Composer 
Monster Logo Studios - Sound Effects

Comet is a game for the Playdate Handheld console.
The Playdate is created by Panic Inc
